This repository is an independent open reference implementation of a CID-based reference consistency governance model for static publishing and offline content governance environments.

It is not an HL7 project, not an implementation of HL7 FHIR, not a FHIR Implementation Guide, not a FHIR profile, and not a non-medical edition of FHIR.

FHIR is referenced only as a mature source of selected design concepts, including logical identity, versioned reference, human-readable narrative, controlled coding, and provenance-style auditability.

